497
00:32:12,800 --> 00:32:14,480
You mark my words.

498
00:32:14,520 --> 00:32:17,920
They almost died when they thought
that Chloe had run off with some...

499
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:20,640
...guy that ran a gastropub in the city.

500
00:32:20,720 --> 00:32:22,200
But...

501
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:29,360
You're gonna do very well
for yourself, unless you blow it.

502
00:32:30,520 --> 00:32:32,560
And how am I going to blow it?

503
00:32:36,440 --> 00:32:38,560
By making a pass at me.

504
00:32:40,760 --> 00:32:43,120
And what makes you think
