505
00:32:45,360 --> 00:32:47,720
Men always seem to wonder.

506
00:32:49,560 --> 00:32:52,840
They think I'd be
something very special.

507
00:32:52,920 --> 00:32:54,880
And are you?

508
00:32:58,040 --> 00:33:00,880
Well, no one's ever
asked for their money back.

509
00:33:04,240 --> 00:33:07,400
Where was all this confidence
