520
00:33:54,120 --> 00:33:55,520
Oh, he's so sweet.

521
00:33:55,600 --> 00:33:57,520
The problem with the right hind
is gonna...

522
00:33:57,600 --> 00:33:59,560
It should have dissipated fully already.

523
00:33:59,640 --> 00:34:01,880
- Tom, can I feed him?
- Yeah, yeah, wack him some hay.

524
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:03,520
Tom, do you think he's
gonna be able to play on Sunday?

525
00:34:03,600 --> 00:34:06,480
Well, he will play on Sunday,
but it's just the problem with the fact

526
00:34:06,560 --> 00:34:09,280
that it's only Lopez who can ride him,
and he's injured at the moment.

527
00:34:09,360 --> 00:34:11,200
We're having a bloody nightmare
with injuries.

528
00:34:11,280 --> 00:34:13,280
You're so beautiful.

529
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:18,600
What would you say to the idea
of taking a business course at school

530
00:34:18,680 --> 00:34:20,960
that the company would pay for?

531
00:34:21,040 --> 00:34:22,600
I don't know.

532
00:34:26,320 --> 00:34:29,360
I've had very good
feedback on your work.

533
00:34:29,720 --> 00:34:31,520
And the beginning of next year

534
00:34:31,600 --> 00:34:34,520
