553
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,920
Have you seen my Strindberg book?

554
00:35:32,000 --> 00:35:33,320
No.

555
00:35:33,400 --> 00:35:35,160
How did your audition go?

556
00:35:35,240 --> 00:35:38,520
Oh, it was pretty awful, I'm afraid.

557
00:35:38,560 --> 00:35:41,440
It's her own fault, bless her.
She just tightens up.

558
00:35:41,520 --> 00:35:44,360
Well, I'm sure something
worthwhile will come along.

559
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:48,880
