continually discouraging her via...

584
00:37:02,640 --> 00:37:04,000
...innuendos.

585
00:37:04,080 --> 00:37:06,720
All I'm saying is acting's
so will-o'-the-wisp.

586
00:37:06,800 --> 00:37:08,840
Those that have it, know it right off.

587
00:37:08,880 --> 00:37:11,440
To pursue it because
you don't want to admit defeat

588
00:37:11,520 --> 00:37:14,360
