frankly, unrealistic.

589
00:37:14,440 --> 00:37:16,440
I'm sorry, but that's the way I feel.

590
00:37:17,040 --> 00:37:18,360
Excuse me.

591
00:37:19,000 --> 00:37:20,000
Nola.

592
00:37:20,080 --> 00:37:22,280
It's OK. I'd like to be alone, thanks.

593
00:37:22,360 --> 00:37:25,280
Well, thank you very much. And I'm
sorry if I'm raising my voice now,

594
00:37:25,360 --> 00:37:27,560
but you know that's her
Achilles heel, emotionally.

595
00:37:27,600 --> 00:37:31,160
He's right, Eleanor. I think
you've had one too many G and T's.

596
00:38:47,000 --> 00:38:48,480
I was looking for you.

597
00:38:50,000 --> 00:38:52,640
I was upset.
I just wanted to be alone.

598
00:38:52,720 --> 00:38:54,680
I don't mean to intrude.

599
00:38:55,920 --> 00:38:57,840
I need a drink.

600
00:38:57,920 --> 00:39:00,680
I like you when you drink.
You get flirtatious.

601
00:39:00,760 --> 00:39:02,720
- Do I?
- Yeah.

602
00:39:02,800 --> 00:39:05,160
- Confident.
- I don't think this was a good idea.

603
00:39:05,200 --> 00:39:06,840
You shouldn't have followed me here.

604
00:39:06,920 --> 00:39:08,920
Do you feel guilty?

605
00:39:10,200 --> 00:39:12,200
Do you?

606
00:39:20,200 --> 00:39:22,200
We can't do this.

607
00:39:22,880 --> 00:39:24,840
I know.

608
00:39:32,040 --> 00:39:34,040
This can't lead anyplace.

609
00:40:49,920 --> 00:40:50,920
Hello.

610
00:40:52,000 --> 00:40:53,960
Darling, I think it's for you.

611
00:40:54,960 --> 00:40:56,840
But take it outside.

612
00:41:12,400 --> 00:41:14,480
Well, there's hope, at least.

613
00:41:14,560 --> 00:41:16,720
When's the callback?

614
00:41:18,800 --> 00:41:20,960
Just let me know
when you hear anything at all,

615
00:41:21,040 --> 00:41:24,240
'cause I really think
I could be great in this part.

616
00:41:25,400 --> 00:41:28,120
Yeah. OK.

617
00:41:28,200 --> 00:41:29,280
Bye.

618
00:41:30,040 --> 00:41:32,040
