624
00:41:44,240 --> 00:41:47,200
I mean... The moment was very
out of control for many reasons.

625
00:41:47,280 --> 00:41:49,960
I was upset, I was drinking,
and the storm was overpowering.

626
00:41:50,040 --> 00:41:52,760
- Oh, stop rationalizing.
- I'm not rationalizing.

627
00:41:52,800 --> 00:41:56,880
Passions are passions, but we're
both very involved with other people.

628
00:41:57,320 --> 00:42:00,240
You're not such a good actress,
you know. It's not possible.

629
00:42:00,840 --> 00:42:03,960
Look, you daydreamed
about making love to me,

630
00:42:04,040 --> 00:42:06,840
and I'm not saying the fantasy
didn't cross my mind, OK?

631
00:42:06,880 --> 00:42:08,200
We had our moment.

632
00:42:08,280 --> 00:42:10,760
But, you know, let's move on,
get back to reality.

633
00:42:10,840 --> 00:42:13,080
Chris, we're gonna be
brother and sister-in-law.

634
00:42:13,600 --> 00:42:16,120
You were exactly
as I pictured you'd be making love.

635
00:42:16,200 --> 00:42:18,440
Chris, forget it. It's over.

636
00:42:31,520 --> 00:42:34,080
Thanks. Henry!

637
00:42:34,160 --> 00:42:36,800
- Hey. How are you?
- Chris. All right.

638
00:42:36,880 --> 00:42:38,400
- Look at you.
- Good to see you.

639
00:42:38,480 --> 00:42:40,760
Looks like you're doing
all right for yourself, aren't you?

640
00:42:40,840 --> 00:42:42,560
- Thanks.
- You still doing the tennis tour?

641
00:42:42,640 --> 00:42:44,360
Yeah, I love it. I love it.
Look at this car.

642
00:42:44,440 --> 00:42:46,800
Oh, don't worry, it's not mine.
It's the company's.

643
00:42:46,880 --> 00:42:49,480
Yeah, I know you found it
a bit of a grind, didn't you?

644
00:42:49,520 --> 00:42:52,280
But I'm still circling the globe,
deluding myself.

645
00:42:52,360 --> 00:42:54,080
I just couldn't stand it.

646
00:42:54,160 --> 00:42:56,480
No. No, I heard you went into business.

647
00:42:56,560 --> 00:42:58,760
I'm a wheel in an office,
if you can believe it.

648
00:42:58,840 --> 00:43:01,280
- A big wheel.
- It's who you know, Henry.

649
00:43:01,360 --> 00:43:03,880
