or comes right back at you?

656
00:43:16,960 --> 00:43:18,880
I always admired
your game though, you know?

657
00:43:18,920 --> 00:43:20,360
- Thanks.
- You were very steady.

658
00:43:20,440 --> 00:43:22,040
Cool under pressure, but creative.

659
00:43:22,120 --> 00:43:24,280
You could be a poet
with the racket like Laver was.

660
00:43:24,320 --> 00:43:25,760
I lost to you as much as I beat you.

661
00:43:25,840 --> 00:43:27,640
