668
00:43:40,120 --> 00:43:42,440
- You should call me anytime.
- Very impressive.

669
00:43:42,520 --> 00:43:43,680
So good to see you, Henry.

670
00:43:43,760 --> 00:43:45,120
- You look well.
- And you, mate.

671
00:43:45,200 --> 00:43:46,560
- You look very, very well.
- I can buy us lunch.

672
00:43:46,640 --> 00:43:48,680
- Put it on the expense account, so...
- Very well.

673
00:43:48,760 --> 00:43:49,840
...do call.
- Very good. Yeah, yeah.

674
00:43:49,880 --> 00:43:51,760
- All right.
- Bye.

675
00:43:51,840 --> 00:43:53,200
- Oh, my God.
- Right there.

676
00:43:53,280 --> 00:43:56,520
- She's got glasses on.
- But why on earth?

677
00:43:56,600 --> 00:43:58,600
Why on earth would
your mother invite her here?

678
00:43:58,680 --> 00:44:01,200
She met her at the supermarket
yesterday and invited her...

679
00:44:01,280 --> 00:44:02,280
- The supermarket?
- Yes.

680
00:44:02,360 --> 00:44:04,600
- Can you play the piano?
- No, I'm terrible at the piano.

681
00:44:04,680 --> 00:44:06,720
