having you as a brother-in-law,

692
00:44:27,920 --> 00:44:30,040
and whatever you two need,
you can always rely on us.

693
00:44:30,120 --> 00:44:31,440
I appreciate that.

694
00:45:09,920 --> 00:45:12,080
Darling, one second.
I just think we...

695
00:45:16,400 --> 00:45:18,800
