722
00:46:45,680 --> 00:46:47,680
- Yeah.
- That could be a problem.

723
00:46:49,440 --> 00:46:51,760
I want you to make me pregnant.

724
00:46:52,800 --> 00:46:56,160
Chloe... We discussed this.

